import { Button, Flex, Grid } from '@chakra-ui/core';

const FormLayout = (props) => (
  <Flex
    justify="center"
    flexDirection="column"
    alignItems="center"
    margin="auto"
    width="75%"
  >
    <form method="post" onSubmit={props.handleSubmit}>
      <Grid templateColumns="5fr 1fr">{props.children}</Grid>
    </form>
    <Flex width="75%">
      <Button width="100%">Register</Button>
    </Flex>
  </Flex>
);

export default FormLayout;
